Atomic,Trade,is,a,New,Jersey,based,BitCoin,and,cryptocurrency,exchange,They,allow,users,to,buy,sell,and,trade,major,crypto,currencies,The,Atomic,Trade,API,is,a,free,to,use,open,data,API,that,accepts,HTTP,requests,Individual,calls,will,return,marketplace,data,arrays,such,as,current,cryptocurrency,pricing,a,list,of,active,markets,along,with,coin,volume,and,pricing,recent,orders,issued,through,Atomic,Trade,details,on,trades,since,a,certain,timestamp,and,trade,pair,comparisons,including,price,and,volume,The,data,can,be,implemented,into,rd,party,applications,that,require,cryptocurrency,market,information